|[[File:Zenkoji Temple Kyozo June 27 2007.jpg|thumb|x140px|Revolving shelves at [[Zenkō-ji]]]]
|[[File:Kamakura Hasedera Rotating prayer wheel.jpg|thumb|x148px|''Rinzō'' at [[Hase-dera (Kamakura)|Hase-dera]]]]
|}

